    <h2>Controls</h2>

    <p>
        <b>A</b> moves left.<br>
        <b>D</b> moves right.<br>
        <b>W</b> fires jumpjets.<br>
        <b>Left and right arrows</b> aim.<br>
        <b>Up and down arrows</b> control gun power.<br>
        <b>Space</b> fires.<br>
        <b>Q</b> changes weapon.<br>
        <b>Arrow keys</b> and <b>Enter</b> control the menus.<br>
        <b>T</b> is for chat.<br>
    </p>
